---
title: Red Wine Glazed Lamb Shank with Honey Rosemary Carrots and Roast Potatoes
description: We love good Lamb Shank With Honey Rosemary Carrots and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/red-wine-glazed-lamb-shank-fc7a7a27-9e627e87.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/red-wine-glazed-lamb-shank-5f7f1e8e22e21d6c207f2d67-07c3af68.pdf
